item.title: CVE-2020-7805|2024-08-04T09:41:01.852Z -- infomark -- kt%20slim%20egg%20iml500
item.description: An issue was discovered on KT Slim egg IML500 (R7283, R8112, R8424) and IML520 (R8112, R8368, R8411) wifi device. This issue is a command injection allowing attackers to execute arbitrary OS commands.
